text: Petra Komínková (born 17 November 1951) is a Czech handball player, born in Olomouc. She played for the Czechoslovak national team, and represented Czechoslovakia at the 1980 Summer Olympics in Moscow. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Olomouc Category:Czechoslovak female handball players Category:Olympic handball players of Czechoslovakia Category:Handball players at the 1980 Summer Olympics
